comments: Vassell (SAS) moves his pivot foot heel-to-toe to create space.
Jones (SAS) reaches in and makes clean contact to the ball, and on the follow-through, grazes Sabonis' (SAC) arm, which does not affect his control of the ball at the end of the drive.
Sabonis (SAC) gathers the ball on his left foot and establishes his right foot as his pivot, which he maintains prior to releasing the pass.
Sabonis (SAC) steps forward into Wembanyama (SAS) during his shooting motion, affecting his shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) cleanly blocks Vassell's (SAS) shot attempt near the basket.
Sabonis (SAC) establishes himself in Vassell's (SAS) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Huerter (SAC) absorbs the incoming contact from Jones (SAS) during the drive as he brushes Jones' (SAS) arm, which he is able to move through.
Vassell (SAS) commits a take foul on Monk (SAC).
Sabonis (SAC) is moving alongside Sochan's (SAS) path and the body contact that occurs as they come together during the drive is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) legally contests Sochan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
